{"tid":2226270,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[世界末日] 侵侵高級顧問希克斯確診武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-10-02T02:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-02T03:01:14.000Z","uid":49004,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a47a7d778313aa8d245e96af9cbd2c888ceec6fb","tid":2226270,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T02:44:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1887851/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1887851%2F&d=NeqW8uJC54Uj1%2BY3pyrdAvjlBAU1VhUdv3lOLHlSYeE%3D&h=f6080bb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1887851%2F&h=ba9c306f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1887851/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國傳媒引述消息報道，總統特朗普的高級顧問希克斯確診<del>新冠</del>武漢肺炎，並出現病徵。據報指，<span class=\"red\">希克斯早前多次陪同特朗普出席活動，包括周二晚一同乘搭空軍一號專機到俄亥俄州，出席首場總統選舉電視辯論，以及前日一同到明尼蘇達州出席集會。</span><br />\n<br />\n白宮發言人暫未有確認是否有職員確診，只表示特朗普重視個人、支持者及民眾的健康，而白宮一直遵循疾控中心指引。<br />\n<br />\n希克斯在2016年曾擔任白宮通訊總監，又協助特朗普進行競選活動，之後轉到私人機構，今年初重返白宮。"},{"pid":"309ab8344db0d9992cbfe7f627bb9906e46d0dcd","tid":2226270,"uid":272422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T02:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 某國想用生物武器殺Trump?"},{"pid":"13c0a5ff1bec29e00fad703f0b7549c936fd8194","tid":2226270,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T02:51:56.000Z","msg":"牙侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好死"},{"pid":"4dc04a4643abe4232dd1fe05149d6a22c6a8d0e4","tid":2226270,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13c0a5ff1bec29e00fad703f0b7549c936fd8194","tid":2226270,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T02:51:56.000